OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778061972
OL,3,CBistro losing footfall after burst
OL,4,Cwater main leaves busy road closed
OL,6,FA Hampshire cafe owner says they're
OL,7,Flosing footfall because of a burst
OL,8,Fwater main which has left a major
OL,9,Froute between Botley and Whiteley
OL,10,Fclosed.
OL,12,FPinkmead Bistro and Tearooms on King's
OL,13,FCorner at the edge of Botley Road in
OL,14,FCurdridge said since the incident on
OL,15,FSaturday, customer numbers have
OL,16,Fdropped as there's no way of people
OL,17,Fknowing if they are open and the best
OL,18,Froute to take.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
