OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778061972
OL,3,CBistro losing footfall after burst
OL,4,Cwater main leaves busy road closed
OL,6,FPart of Botley Road was closed after
OL,7,Fthe main burst on Saturday morning,
OL,8,Fleaving nearby residents and
OL,9,Fbusinesses without water or low
OL,10,Fpressure.
OL,12,FVideos from the scene revealed water
OL,13,Fshooting up into the air, leaving
OL,14,Froads looking more like rivers.
OL,16,FBut it happened again on bank holiday
OL,17,FMonday, causing even more disruption.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778061972
OL,3,CBistro losing footfall after burst
OL,4,Cwater main leaves busy road closed
OL,6,FWorkers from Southern Water are on
OL,7,Fsite carrying out repairs, but the
OL,8,Froad is expected to remain closed for
OL,9,Fseveral more days.
OL,11,FSpeaking to ITV Meridian Hend Elhouni
OL,12,Ffrom Pinkmead said: "I think it's the
OL,13,Funcertainty because a lot of our
OL,14,Fcustomers, our regulars and new
OL,15,Fcustomers, they don't know if actually
OL,16,Fwe're open.
OL,18,F"There hasn't been very good signage
OL,19,Faround to kind of indicate to people
OL,20,Fif we are open for business as usual.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778061972
OL,3,CBistro losing footfall after burst
OL,4,Cwater main leaves busy road closed
OL,6,F"We've had to kind of just put out the
OL,7,Fword ourselves constantly to let
OL,8,Fpeople in the local area and people
OL,9,Fwho want to come and visit know that
OL,10,Fwe are open, and guide them on which
OL,11,Fis the best route for them to come to
OL,12,Four bistro."
OL,14,FIt's not the first time the bistro has
OL,15,Fbeen affected.
OL,17,FHend added that on top of the
OL,18,Fdisruption from the plans for the
OL,19,FBotley bypass at the end of the month
OL,20,F- they are feeling frustrated.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778061972
OL,3,CBistro losing footfall after burst
OL,4,Cwater main leaves busy road closed
OL,6,F"We're not particularly happy about it
OL,7,Fbecause it's for the whole of half
OL,8,Fterm, which is normally a very busy
OL,9,Ftime for us.
OL,11,F"So to have this on top of that is
OL,12,Fjust kind of an added inconvenience
OL,13,Freally.
OL,15,F"We've kind of thought okay we'll
OL,16,Fprobably write off May completely
OL,17,Fbecause you know there's always going
OL,18,Fto be one thing or the other.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778061972
OL,3,CBistro losing footfall after burst
OL,4,Cwater main leaves busy road closed
OL,6,F"People are really put off by the
OL,7,Froadworks and the diversions and they
OL,8,Fjust can't be bothered really to kind
OL,9,Fof see if it's going to be worth
OL,10,Fcoming here or not."
OL,12,FStaff at the bistro are urging people
OL,13,Fto visit and reassuring residents they
OL,14,Fare open for business.
OL,16,F"We would like to encourage people to
OL,17,Fcome and visit us and not be put off
OL,18,Fby the roadworks," Hend added.
OL,20,F"We will always be here.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778061972
OL,3,CBistro losing footfall after burst
OL,4,Cwater main leaves busy road closed
OL,6,F"If they are in any doubt they can
OL,7,Falways give us a call and just check
OL,8,Fthat we are open."
OL,10,FOne resident described the weekend
OL,11,Fwithout water as "difficult."
OL,13,F"I went and stocked up with water,"
OL,14,Fshe said.
OL,16,F"Trying to have showers, was your hair
OL,17,Fthings like that - it's been awful.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778061972
OL,3,CBistro losing footfall after burst
OL,4,Cwater main leaves busy road closed
OL,6,F"We got a text through from Southern
OL,7,FWater about an hour and a half after
OL,8,Fwe lost water - we tried to report it
OL,9,Fonline but it wouldn't let me.
OL,11,F"We weren't told anything - only
OL,12,Frealised when we turned the tap on.
OL,13,FYou just don't realise how much it
OL,14,Faffects everything.
OL,16,F"It's not good - especially twice in a
OL,17,Fweek."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
