OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778061972
OL,3,CBistro losing footfall after burst
OL,4,Cwater main leaves busy road closed
OL,6,FA Southern Water spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"Our teams have repaired a burst water
OL,8,Fmain on the Botley Road, Southampton,
OL,9,Fwhich started on 2 May.
OL,11,F"The temporary road closure will be in
OL,12,Fplace until engineers finish the
OL,13,Freinstatement work, which is scheduled
OL,14,Fto be complete before the end of this
OL,15,Fweek.
OL,17,F"We're sorry for the inconvenience
OL,18,Fthis has caused residents and
OL,19,Fcommuters during this time, and we
OL,20,Fthank them for their patience."
OL,26,@oD@AOU|D@_O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/10
